      </table>      <span class="plaintext"><a href="../parents.htm">Parents of Penguins</a> &gt; Q &amp; A for Parents </span><a href="http://www.bbbonline.org/cks.asp?id=30601091152963567" target="_blank"><br>
                </a><h1>Q &amp; A for Parents </h1>
                <div align="left">
                  <ul>
                    <li class="plaintext"><a href="#" onClick="return goAnchor('what-is')">What is Club Penguin?</a></li>
